› how to provde it is installed succesfully


• Run these in PowerShell.
                                                                                                                       
  For the current terminal session first set:                                                                          
                                                                                                                       
  $env:PYTHONUTF8='1'                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  Then verify the install:                                                                                             
                                                                                                                       
  Get-Command agent-reach                                                                                              
  agent-reach doctor                                                                                                   
  mcporter.cmd config list                                                                                             
  Get-Command rdt                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                       
  What success looks like:                                                                                             
                                                                                                                       
  - Get-Command agent-reach should point to c:/users/llm.local/bin/agent-reach.exe                                     
  - mcporter.cmd config list should show exa from C:/Users/llm.mcporter/mcporter.json                                  
  - Get-Command rdt should point to c:/users/llm.local/bin/rdt.exe                                                     
  - agent-reach doctor should show the core channels as available                                                      
                                                                                                                       
  On this machine, the successful check showed these as working:                                                       
                                                                                                                       
  - GitHub                                                                                                             
  - YouTube                                                                                                            
  - Reddit                                                                                                             
  - WeChat articles                                                                                                    
  - V2EX                                                                                                               
  - RSS                                                                                                                
  - Exa web search                                                                                                     
  - Generic web reading                                                                                                
  - Bilibili basic support                                                                                             
                                                                                                                       
  If you want a single proof command, use:                                                                             
                                                                                                                       
  $env:PYTHONUTF8='1'; agent-reach doctor                                                                              
                                                                                                                       
  If you want, I can also give you a stricter end-to-end checklist with one real command per channel. 
  
  
  
  
=============================

如何使用：

• agent-reach has two jobs:
                                                                                                                       
  1. manage channels and credentials                                                                                   
  2. install the real tools you use day to day                                                                         
                                                                                                                       
  On this Windows machine, start with this in PowerShell for the current session:                                      
                                                                                                                       
  $env:PYTHONUTF8='1'                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  Manage Agent Reach                                                                                                   
  Use these commands:                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  agent-reach doctor                                                                                                   
  agent-reach setup                                                                                                    
  agent-reach install --channels=twitter,weibo                                                                         
  agent-reach configure --from-browser chrome                                                                          
  agent-reach configure twitter-cookies "cookie_string_here"                                                           
  agent-reach configure groq-key gsk_xxx                                                                               
  agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port                                                                 
                                                                                                                       
  What they do:                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                       
  - doctor: check what works                                                                                           
  - setup: interactive wizard                                                                                          
  - install --channels=...: add optional platforms                                                                     
  - configure: add cookies, keys, proxy, or import from browser                                                        
                                                                                                                       
  Use the installed tools
  After setup, you usually use the upstream tools directly.                                                            
                                                                                                                       
  Web search via Exa:                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  mcporter.cmd call 'exa.web_search_exa(query: "best local llm tools", numResults: 5)'                                 
                                                                                                                       
  Read any webpage:                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                       
  curl.exe https://r.jina.ai/http://example.com                                                                        
                                                                                                                       
  Search Reddit:                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                       
  rdt search "ollama vs lm studio" -n 5 --compact                                                                      
                                                                                                                       
  Read a Reddit post:                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  rdt read <post_id>                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                       
  YouTube metadata/subtitles:                                                                                          
                                                                                                                       
  yt-dlp --dump-json "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEO_ID"                                                        
  yt-dlp --write-auto-sub --skip-download "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEO_ID"
                                                                                                                       
  Bilibili basic:                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                       
  yt-dlp --dump-json "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BVxxxx"                                                           
                                                                                                                       
  A couple of Windows-specific notes:                                                                                  
                                                                                                                       
  - use mcporter.cmd, not mcporter, because PowerShell script execution is restricted here                             
  - if agent-reach doctor or rdt throws encoding errors, run $env:PYTHONUTF8='1' first                                 
  - for full GitHub features, re-auth with gh auth login                                                               
                                                                                                                       
  If you want, I can give you a “first 5 commands to try” workflow for your setup. 
  
  
  
=================


